&lt;h1 class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;🐾 &lt;strong&gt;Love animals? Looking for a career where every day is different?&lt;/strong&gt; 🩺&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chessie Lane Animal Hospital&lt;/strong&gt; in &lt;strong&gt;Ottawa, Illinois&lt;/strong&gt; is growing, and we&#39;re looking for an enthusiastic &lt;strong&gt;Veterinary Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; to join our incredible team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re someone who loves caring for pets, thrives in a fast-paced environment, and enjoys being part of a team that truly has each other&#39;s backs, keep reading. 👇&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;✨ Supporting our veterinarians and veterinary technicians with patient care&lt;br&gt;✨ Helping educate pet parents and making sure they feel informed and confident about their pet&#39;s care&lt;br&gt;✨ Assisting with appointments, treatments, and keeping patients comfortable throughout their visit&lt;br&gt;✨ Caring for our boarding guests by feeding, walking, monitoring, and making them feel at home&lt;br&gt;✨ Cleaning and maintaining kennels, treatment areas, exam rooms, and the hospital to keep everything running smoothly&lt;br&gt;✨ Restraining patients safely during exams and procedures&lt;br&gt;✨ Restocking supplies, preparing rooms, and jumping in wherever the team needs you&lt;br&gt;✨ Delivering compassionate care and creating a positive experience for every pet and every client&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;No two days are the same, and that&#39;s exactly what makes this role so rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;🐶 Has a genuine passion for animal care&lt;br&gt;💬 Loves connecting with people and providing great client education&lt;br&gt;🤝 Works well in a team and is always willing to lend a hand&lt;br&gt;⚡ Stays organized and positive in a busy environment&lt;br&gt;🩺 Has veterinary experience (preferred, but we&#39;d love to meet motivated candidates eager to learn!)&lt;br&gt;📅 Is available to work Saturdays&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why Chessie Lane?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;❤️ A supportive team that genuinely enjoys working together&lt;br&gt;📈 Opportunities to grow your skills and career&lt;br&gt;💰 Competitive pay and benefits&lt;br&gt;🎉 A fun, positive workplace where your work truly makes a difference&lt;br&gt;🐾 Daily puppy cuddles, kitten snuggles, and rewarding moments with pets and their families&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re ready to build a career helping animals while working with an amazing team, we&#39;d love to meet you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apply today and come grow with us. Questions? Contact our clinical staff recruiter at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:ashley@obrienvetgroup.com&quot;&gt;ashley@obrienvetgroup.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

