&lt;p data-start=&quot;67&quot; data-end=&quot;115&quot;&gt;📍 Chessie Lane Animal Clinic | Ottawa, Illinois&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;117&quot; data-end=&quot;376&quot;&gt;Looking for a job where you actually &lt;em data-start=&quot;154&quot; data-end=&quot;160&quot;&gt;want&lt;/em&gt; to come to work? 👀At Chessie Lane Animal Hospital we’re more than a vet clinic, we’re a team of animal lovers, problem-solvers, snack-bringers, chaos coordinators, and professional pet-hype people. 🐾&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;378&quot; data-end=&quot;574&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;398&quot; data-end=&quot;437&quot;&gt;Client Service Representative (CSR)&lt;/strong&gt; full- time position, who can keep the front desk running smoothly while making every pet parent feel welcome, heard and cared for.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;576&quot; data-end=&quot;705&quot;&gt;If you love animals, thrive in a fast-paced environment and can multitask without losing your cool, you might fit right in here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;j1xnej&quot; data-start=&quot;707&quot; data-end=&quot;741&quot;&gt;What You’ll Actually Be Doing:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;742&quot; data-end=&quot;1257&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1d755ou&quot; data-start=&quot;742&quot; data-end=&quot;789&quot;&gt;Greeting pets and their humans like VIPs 🐶🐱&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wk

&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;2378&quot; data-end=&quot;2477&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;186&quot; data-end=&quot;217&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;79&quot;&gt;Veterinary Practice Manager&lt;br data-start=&quot;31&quot; data-end=&quot;34&quot;&gt;Chessie Lane Animal Hospital – Ottawa, IL&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1ln8o0v&quot; data-start=&quot;81&quot; data-end=&quot;94&quot;&gt;Overview:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;95&quot; data-end=&quot;519&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;95&quot; data-end=&quot;127&quot;&gt;Chessie Lane Animal Hospital&lt;/strong&gt; in &lt;strong data-start=&quot;131&quot; data-end=&quot;151&quot;&gt;Ottawa, Illinois&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking an experienced and motivated &lt;strong data-start=&quot;192&quot; data-end=&quot;212&quot;&gt;Practice Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to oversee the daily operations of our growing veterinary hospital. This is a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;291&quot; data-end=&quot;319&quot;&gt;hands-on leadership role&lt;/strong&gt; where you&#39;ll work alongside our veterinary team, support staff, and medical leadership to ensure exceptional patient care, outstanding client service, and a positive, collaborative workplace culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;14uqk01&quot; data-start=&quot;521&quot; data-end=&quot;546&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;548&quot; data-end=&quot;1256&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jugiqw&quot; data-start=&quot;548&quot; data-end=&quot;659&quot;&gt;Oversee daily hospital operations to ensure efficient workflow and exceptional patient and client experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;cru64x&quot; data-start=&quot;660&quot; data-end=&quot;771&quot;&gt;Lead, coach, and support a team of veterinary professionals, fostering accountability and professional growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1vqnt1m&quot; data-start=&quot;772&quot; data-end=&quot;869&quot;&gt;Partner with the Medical Director to support high-quality patient care and hospital initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;i8jh6o&quot; data-start=&quot;870&quot; data-end=&quot;933&quot;&gt;Provide hands-on assistance throughout the hospital as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;i2m56r&quot; data-start=&quot;934&quot; data-end=&quot;1010&quot;&gt;Manage staff scheduling, inventory, purchasing, and operational efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;9lj6hs&quot; data-start=&quot;1011&quot; data-end=&quot;1099&quot;&gt;Monitor financial performance, hospital metrics, and key performance indicators (KPIs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;174ry9y&quot; data-start=&quot;1100&quot; data-end=&quot;1159&quot;&gt;Recruit, onboard, train, and retain talented team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;179p3mi&quot; data-start=&quot;1160&quot; data-end=&quot;1256&quot;&gt;Promote a positive, team-focused culture built on communication, collaboration, and compassion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1obkcim&quot; data-start=&quot;1258&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1279&quot; data-end=&quot;1769&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jxqvsa&quot; data-start=&quot;1279&quot; data-end=&quot;1406&quot;&gt;2+ years of leadership or management experience in veterinary medicine, healthcare, or a customer service-focused environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11lx9o2&quot; data-start=&quot;1407&quot; data-end=&quot;1502&quot;&gt;Veterinary practice experience strongly preferred; veterinary technician experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;yup9m&quot; data-start=&quot;1503&quot; data-end=&quot;1567&quot;&gt;Excellent leadership, communication, and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kogevs&quot; data-start=&quot;1568&quot; data
